I'll move layout tokens to the theme, add safe-area handling, and support split view.```tsx
import { useSafeAreaInsets } from 'react-native-safe-area-context';
import { useResponsiveValue } from '@/hooks/layout/useResponsiveValue';

const containerStyle = React.useMemo(() => ({
  flexDirection: isTablet ? 'row' : 'column',
  gap: theme.spacing.lg,
  paddingHorizontal: theme.spacing.xl,
  paddingTop: insets.top + theme.spacing.lg
}), [isTablet, theme, insets]);
```

I'll complement that with a media query hook and focus management.```tsx
const headerId = React.useId();
React.useEffect(() => {
  AccessibilityInfo.setAccessibilityFocus(headerRef.current);
}, [persona.id]);
```
